org.educraft.block.calculator

Class BlockCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.block.Block
      • net.minecraft.block.BlockContainer
        • org.educraft.block.calculator.BlockCalculator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.minecraft.block.ITileEntityProvider

    public class BlockCalculator
extends net.minecraft.block.BlockContainer
    This class implements a block that can be used to perform calculations. It is based on BlockWorkbench, but with different mechanics.
